dc_creator_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Economic Development
dc_description_s: Brochure about New Jersey's state forests, parks and historic sites. Outside cover features a state map showing each location and major highways. Table shows acreage and facilitities available to the public at each site for bathing, boating, camping, fishing and hunting. The remainder of sheet consist of the first paragraphs of a description of all the sites titled Invitation to State Forests, Parks and Historic Site.
